    "en": {
      "title": "Prof. Udith K. Jayasinghe returns to Wayamba University",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Senior Professor Udith K to be appointed Vice Chancellor of Wayamba University Jayasinghe has been re-appointed.",
        "President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa handed over the appointment letter to Jayasinghe this morning (29) at the President's House, Fort.",
        "Udith K. Mr. Jayasinghe previously held the post from October 2020 to June 2021, after which he also served as the Secretary to the Ministry of Agriculture."
      ],
